bilingual.source: The room was in complete disorder after the party.

bilingual.source: The sudden storm caused disorder in the city.

bilingual.source: The teacher tried to control the disorder in the classroom.
bilingual.target: 老师试图控制教室里的混乱局面。

bilingual.source: Many people misunderstand anarchism as chaos and disorder.
bilingual.target: 许多人误解无政府主义为混乱和无序。

bilingual.source: The traffic disorder made it difficult to get to work on time.
bilingual.target: 交通混乱使得准时上班变得困难。

bilingual.source: In physics, entropy is a measure of the disorder of a system.
bilingual.target: 在物理学中，熵是衡量系统混乱程度的一个指标。

bilingual.source: Tim Harford is author of Messy: The Power of Disorder to Transform Our Lives.
bilingual.target: 蒂姆·哈福德是《混乱：无序改变我们生活的力量》一书的作者。

list.abstract: 《Disorder》是一款网易游戏独立研发的团队竞技射击类手游。 《Disorder》游戏中包括导弹井争夺、据点攻防、团队占领等多种玩法模式，玩家通过抢滩登陆、攻占据点获取经验物资，防具购买枪械升级。同时玩家可以三人、五人小队组排模式，争夺据点、掠夺物资，体验团队作战。 《Disorder》于2020年6月5日11点到2020年6月14日22点进行删档测试，所有测试数据在测试之后进行删除。

yingyinNormal.en: I did what I did to protect people. Our enemies are your enemies, Nick. Disorder, war.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我做的一切都是为了保护人类。我们的敌人就是你的敌人。混乱，战争。

yingyinNormal.en: Say colony collapse disorder keeps on happening, and all the bees get wiped out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蜂群崩坏症候群不断的发生，然后所有的蜜蜂都死了。

yingyinNormal.en: It says the girl died there. Genetic disorder. Galatians Syndrome. And the boy disappears.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其中女婴死了。死因是遗传紊乱。格雷西综合症。而男婴消失了。

yingyinNormal.en: It was David Hackenberg who first alerted the world to a phenomenon called colony collapse disorder. Are they dead?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大卫·哈肯伯格首先提醒世界一种现象，叫做蜂群崩坏症候群。他们死了吗?

yingyinNormal.en: Despite the negative effects, MDMA is being studied as a potential therapy for posttraumatic stress disorder and anxiety.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除了这些负面影响，研究显示摇头丸有机会成为治疗创伤后压力症候群和焦虑症的药物。

yingyinNormal.en: First things first, these movements that you see are from a neurological disorder I suffer from, called tardive dyskinesia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，我这些无意的动作是一种神经障碍疾病导致的，叫迟发性运动障碍。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we don't discriminate here. If people vote against our merger, I'm sure it'll be for other reasons than your disorder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们这里不搞歧视，如果有人投票反对合并，我确定是有其他原因而不是你的障碍。

yingyinNormal.en: A lot of people agree with David's theory. But the scientific jury's still out on exactly what's causing colony collapse disorder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很多人同意大卫的理论。但科学家仍然在努力研究到底是什么造成了蜂群崩坏症候群。

yingyinNormal.en: A friend at the School of Pharmacology gave me these new pills they're testing. He says it's the next big thing for social anxiety disorder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在药学院的一个朋友给了我这些他们正在测试的药，他说这将是治疗社交焦虑障碍领域的又一奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: We are testing a new medication for social anxiety, panic attacks, agoraphobia and obsessive compulsive disorder. Why would they be looking for test subjects here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们正在测试一种新药，专治社交焦虑症恐慌发作症，陌生环境恐怖症和强迫症，他们为什么要在这招人？

yingyinNormal.en: It's what we think caused your narcissistic personality disorder. We discussed it at length during our last video chat. Although how we got onto the subject of you is baffling.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们认为正是这一点引起了你的自恋型人格障碍，我们上次视频聊天时详细地探讨了这个问题。虽然不知道为什么会提到你。
